         <abstract id="aspace_063a216f3c8f9f4b97538ebab143ac85">This collection consists of costume and scenic design sketches submitted by Yale School of Drama students for the Gordon J. Micunis and Jay A. Korbin Scholarship, 1987-1993.</abstract>
