      <acqinfo id="aspace_811899652707b5ec3546529c43cadc95">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>Donated to the Drama Library by the Yale School of Drama in 2004. The collections of the former Drama Library became part of the Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library in 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
