      <scopecontent id="aspace_6254a5c7c8c5014513b296469a9eda62">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains costume and scenic design sketches many of which were submitted by Yale School of Drama students for the Gordon J. Micunis and Jay A. Korbin Scholarship.</p>  
